http://www.conservative.org:80/free/ST93/UserFees93.html 204.71.237.88 19970208144455 text/html 6664
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 14:45:37 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:13:37 GMT
Content-length: 6479
