http://www.conservative.org:80/free/ST93/Business93.html 204.71.237.88 19970208144708 text/html 6996
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 14:47:53 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:12:14 GMT
Content-length: 6811
