<DOCHDR>
http://www.conservative.org:80/free/ST96/NWEA.ST1996.html 204.71.237.88 19970208143923 text/html 7752
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 14:39:53 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 15-Jul-96 13:59:44 GMT
Content-length: 7567
