HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Server: Netscape-Commerce/1.12
Date: Saturday, 08-Feb-97 14:48:24 GMT
Last-modified: Monday, 01-Jul-96 01:13:13 GMT
Content-length: 6622
Content-type: text/html
